в”Ӯ ## Initial Observations ##                                                                 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ The reproducer is already minimized. Based on my experience in debugging these bugs, the   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ issue is likely introduced by the *first transformation*, or due to incorrect analysis     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ information feeding into it.                                                               в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ Here, the *first transformation* means the *first transformation point* that modifies the  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ IR in the pass regardless of whether it's in the `instcombine` module or other modules.    в”Ӯ
