в”Ӯ ### Tool Call Format ###                                                                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ When using a tool, return a JSON object strictly following below format:                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ <tool_call>                                                                                в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ {                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   "name": <tool_name>,                                                                     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   "args": <tool_args>                                                                      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ }                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ </tool_call>                                                                               в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ For example:                                                                               в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ <tool_call>                                                                                в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ {                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   "name": "get_weather",                                                                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   "args": {                                                                                в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     "location": "New York",                                                                в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     "date": "2023-10-01",                                                                  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     "celsius": true                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ   }                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ }                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ </tool_call>                                                                               в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ ### Key Requirements ###                                                                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 1. ALWAYS wrap your response with "<tool_call>" and "</tool_call>" as shown above so that  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ I know you are calling a tool.                                                             в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 2. Content inside "<tool_call>" and "</tool_call>" MUST be a valid JSON object. Put all    в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ other content outside of these tags.                                                       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 3. The "args" field MUST also be a valid JSON object. It is NOT a string that represents a в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ JSON object.                                                                               в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 4. Only call ONE tool in each of your response. Do NOT call multiple tools at the same     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ time.                                                                                      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                            в”Ӯ
