в”Ӯ 0`. The optimization incorrectly assumes that if the `select` operates on vectors, its     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ condition must also be a vector.                                                           в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                                                                                            в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ The fix is to ensure type compatibility by splatting the scalar condition into a vector of в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ the same width as the other operands before creating the new binary instruction. This      в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ needs to be done for two similar transformation patterns within the                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ `foldICmpBinOpEqualityWithConstant` function.                                              в”Ӯ
