в”Ӯ   }                                                                                        в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ }                                                                                          в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ </tool_call>                                                                               в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ This change correctly identifies the problematic pattern and prevents the transform, thus  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ avoiding the crash. It is a more targeted fix that respects the existing performance       в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ heuristic in the test suite. I will now verify this fix.                                   в”Ӯ
